\f1\b sun
\f0\b0 's glare prevented earthlings from watching the show. However, coronographs on the Solar and Heliospheric Observatory captured the sequence. A movie of the spectacle is posted on the web. The animation shows three coronal mass ejections. Although Mars appears close to the 
